---
import BasicLayout from '../layouts/BasicLayout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import profileImage from '../assets/profile.jpeg';
---

<BasicLayout title="Accueil">
	<main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-14">
		<!-- Hero / Intro -->
		<section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-green-200/60 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 via-white to-emerald-50 p-8 md:p-10 mb-20">
			<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 [background:radial-gradient(circle_at_80%_20%,rgba(16,185,129,.18),transparent_60%)]"></div>
			<div class="flex flex-col-reverse items-start gap-10 md:flex-row md:items-center">
				<div class="relative z-10">
					<h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-5xl">
						Kelian Cazeneuve
					</h1>
					<p class="mt-3 text-xl font-medium text-emerald-700">
						Créateur d’expériences visuelles & interactives
					</p>
					<p class="mt-5 max-w-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						Étudiant en 3ᵉ année de BUT MMI. Je conçois des interfaces, des univers 3D et des contenus audiovisuels qui unissent esthétique, clarté et immersion. En recherche d’un stage dès février 2025 pour renforcer une équipe créative.
					</p>
					<div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
						<a href="blog/" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-emerald-700 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-emerald-500">
							<span>Voir mes projets</span>
							<svg class="h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
							</svg>
						</a>
						<a href="cv" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-emerald-300/70 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-emerald-400 hover:bg-emerald-50 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-emerald-500">
							<svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 4h10l3 4v12a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H7a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1z" />
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11 10h5M11 14h5" />
							</svg>
							<span>Mon CV</span>
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="relative mx-auto shrink-0">
					<div class="relative">
						<Image
							src={profileImage}
							alt="Photo de profil de Kelian Cazeneuve"
							class="h-40 w-40 md:h-48 md:w-48 rounded-full object-cover ring-4 ring-white shadow-lg border border-emerald-200"
							width={192}
							height={192}
							loading="eager"
						/>
						<span class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-white shadow">
							Disponible stage
							<span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
								<span class="absolute inline-flex h-full w-full animate-ping rounded-full bg-white/70"></span>
								<span class="relative inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-white"></span>
							</span>
						</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="absolute inset-x-10 -bottom-6 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400/10 via-emerald-600/10 to-emerald-400/10 blur-2xl"></div>
		</section>

		<!-- About -->
		<section class="mb-20 fade-in" data-delay="0">
			<header class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
				<div class="h-8 w-1 rounded bg-emerald-600"></div>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">À propos</h2>
			</header>
			<div class="prose max-w-none prose-emerald">
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
					Passionné par le design, l’UI/UX et la création 3D, j’aime donner vie à des idées en mêlant esthétique et technique. Que ce soit pour un site, une animation ou un univers immersif, je cherche toujours à créer quelque chose de clair, fluide et agréable à utiliser.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
					En 2025, je veux rejoindre une équipe créative où je pourrai concevoir, animer et intégrer des interfaces tout en continuant à progresser.				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Skills -->
		<section class="mb-20 fade-in" data-delay="100">
			<header class="mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
				<div class="h-8 w-1 rounded bg-emerald-600"></div>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Compétences & Outils</h2>
			</header>
			<div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
				<div class="group rounded-xl border border-emerald-100/60 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md">
					<h3 class="mb-3 flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-emerald-700">
						<span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
						Front-end
					</h3>
					<ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
						{['HTML','CSS','JavaScript','Accessibilité','Performance'].map(item => (
							<li class="rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-700 ring-1 ring-emerald-200/70">{item}</li>
						))}
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="group rounded-xl border border-emerald-100/60 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md">
					<h3 class="mb-3 flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-emerald-700">
						<span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
						Design & UI
					</h3>
					<ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
						{['Figma','Photoshop','Illustrator','Typographie','Design System'].map(item => (
							<li class="rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-700 ring-1 ring-emerald-200/70">{item}</li>
						))}
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="group rounded-xl border border-emerald-100/60 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md">
					<h3 class="mb-3 flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-emerald-700">
						<span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
						Audiovisuel & 3D
					</h3>
					<ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
						{['Premiere Pro','After Effects','Blender','Storyboard','Motion'].map(item => (
							<li class="rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-700 ring-1 ring-emerald-200/70">{item}</li>
						))}
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Mini teaser Projets -->
		<section class="mb-16 fade-in" data-delay="150">
			<header class="mb-6 flex items-center justify-between">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Aperçu de projets</h2>
				<a href="blog/" class="text-sm font-medium text-emerald-700 hover:underline inline-flex items-center gap-1">
					Tout voir
					<svg class="h-3 w-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
					</svg>
				</a>
			</header>
			<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
				{[
					{titre:'Refonte interface', tag:'UI/UX'},
					{titre:'Animation identité', tag:'Motion'},
					{titre:'Scène 3D immersive', tag:'Blender'}
				].map(card => (
					<a href="blog/" class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md">
						<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/10 to-emerald-600/20 transition"></div>
						<p class="text-sm font-medium text-emerald-600">{card.tag}</p>
						<h3 class="mt-2 font-semibold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-emerald-700">{card.titre}</h3>
						<span class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-700">
							Voir
							<svg class="h-3 w-3 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
							</svg>
						</span>
					</a>
				))}
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- CTA final -->
		<section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-emerald-200/70 bg-white p-10 text-center fade-in" data-delay="200">
			<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_30%_70%,rgba(16,185,129,0.15),transparent_60%)]"></div>
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">Intéressé pour collaborer ?</h2>
			<p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-gray-600">
				Si vous cherchez quelqu’un pour un stage, je serais ravi d’apporter mon approche mêlant design, motion et prototypage à vos projets.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
				<a href="blog/" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-emerald-700">
					Mes projets
					<svg class="h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
					</svg>
				</a>
				<a href="cv" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-emerald-300 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-50">
					Mon CV
				</a>
				<a href="mailto:kelian.cazeneuve@etu.unilim.fr" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-transparent bg-emerald-50 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-emerald-100">
					Me contacter
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<!-- Simple fade-in on scroll -->
	<script>
		const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
			entries.forEach(e => {
				if (e.isIntersecting) {
					e.target.classList.add('opacity-100','translate-y-0');
					observer.unobserve(e.target);
				}
			});
		}, { threshold: 0.15 });

		document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in').forEach((el) => {
			el.style.transition = 'opacity .7s ease, transform .7s ease';
			el.style.transitionDelay = (el.dataset.delay || 0) + 'ms';
			el.classList.add('opacity-0','translate-y-6');
			observer.observe(el);
		});
	</script>
</BasicLayout>